{"tid":45600,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［譚仔請入一入黎］譚仔辣度問題［三哥都歡迎架］","createTime":"2016-12-19T05:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T04:51:31.000Z","uid":32322,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f91236a753069fda433fd766afa3d686f09d819f","tid":45600,"uid":32322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n炎仔#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc 嘗試用數學角度去研究譚仔辣度既問題：<br />\n小辣=落1滴辣油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十小辣=10x小辣<br />\n十小辣=落10滴辣油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但事實話我知十小辣只係十份一小辣咁辣，如果小辣辣過十小辣，點解十小辣係十小辣，而唔係十份一小辣？咁十小辣要用幾多滴辣油？點量度？<br />\n<br />\n好啦 咁當辣度前面個數係=辣度既份母，e.g. 10小辣=1/10小辣，咁三特辣=1/3特辣？#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <br />\n<br />\n但如果三特辣係1/3特辣，咁究竟三特辣有幾辣？大辣辣d定三特辣辣d?<br />\n<br />\n當我懷疑譚仔呀姐唔識計數時，佢收錢又收得岩架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc <br />\n<br />\n炎仔求指教#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"6106151e393b2dd23cff3c6883251d678798b4b4","tid":45600,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe0d4de18f187bb2ca9a593af688f616cf46dc7","tid":45600,"uid"