"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"揸完車好想食譚仔"},{"pid":"2cbe7a266aff316424e0b54d369f8a7ed7557989","tid":45600,"uid":54819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢一小辣到十小辣都未必係linear scale架啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係譚仔做過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dfc7acfb76a17d02b7bebda5d13d5ad5dc9ff8","tid":45600,"uid":54819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢一小辣到十小辣都未必係linear scale架啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係譚仔做過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係如果10小係1滴，1小係10滴<br />\nvs 10小 1/10滴，一小01/1滴<br />\n個scale已經唔同左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以係咪應該搵佢個scale出尼先，會實際d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13667a7d598283f24486aef2a400005a55e36e3b","tid":45600,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"辣字多到觸發咗完型崩壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申食開清湯底"},{"pid":"97e5420e8b21670437d291d9744b8ce318c2de86","tid":45600,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"食十小辣都口水鼻涕流曬，點睇。"}]}